Voidex SDK — derived work
=========================

This package is a fork of opencode's `@opencode-ai/sdk` package (the TypeScript
SDK for the opencode HTTP/WebSocket server). The original source is
distributed by opencode under the MIT license; the original copyright remains
with its authors:

  Copyright (c) opencode authors (https://opencode.ai)

For Voidex we plan to either wrap or replace the transport so calls route to
`void serve` (the local Hono server introduced by void-cli PR #80). Until that
adapter lands the SDK still targets the opencode wire protocol verbatim.

